5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">毕业后的前三年你是怎么在北上广深活下来的？</span></p></li><li><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">未来三十年内，哪些行业的工作人员可能会被人工智能取代？失业的人类何去何从？</span></p></li><li><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">你是怎么有效利用碎片时间的？</span></p></li><li><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">外企，中年失业何去何从？</span></p></li></ul><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Source Han Sans SC&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Source Han Sans SC&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appTj36slmg4002/image/ueditor/60316300_1556268179.png" title=".png" alt="未标题-1-01.png"/></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Source Han Sans SC&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appTj36slmg4002/image/ueditor/95105200_1556268179.png" title=".png" alt="未标题-1-03.png"/></span></p><p st